data.description: Assumable Loan - Welcome to this updated house located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Apple Greene.  The backyard is private, flat, and partially fenced.  The house is roomy with cathedral ceilings in the living and a deck off of the dining room. The kitchen is updated with new appliances and granite countertops. This house offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The primary bedroom has two closets and a separate updated bathroom. You enter the house on the main level which consists of a breeze way with closets, the main level family room is updated with the option to install a full bathroom. There is a lot of potential for this space, install a third full bathroom and use it as a bedroom, use it for a family room, install a bar and use it for an entertaining area.  There is a large separate laundry room. Plenty of room in the one car garage for a car and storage.  Lots of extra parking on the paved driveway.  The roof is less than 5 years old and no HOA.  Perfect for commuters into DC or Virginia.  Easy access to Joint Base Andrews also. Just minutes from all the shopping you need.
